{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"00236dd65f","title":"必须注意欧洲工人的这些特点","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"56e0e5fd79","index":0,"year":1939,"month":11,"day":7,"articleId":"00236dd65f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","name":"斯大林选集（诸夏怀斯社2017年5月）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"斯大林，诸夏怀斯社2017年5月","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"1332d101b8","name":"斯大林"}]},"publication_details":{"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6bc3f85a7d","type":"paragraph","text":"必须注意欧洲工人的这些特点","index":0,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"00236dd65f"},{"id":"431aca24d0","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年11月7日）1939年11月7日","index":1,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"00236dd65f"},{"id":"9c5d76c8e9","type":"paragraph","text":"检阅和游行（人们抬着李米特落夫的画像和几幅台尔受的画像。）","index":2,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"00236dd65f"},{"id":"5cccf56b3d","type":"paragraph","text":"在斯大林那里吃午餐。","index":3,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"00236dd65f"},{"id":"1a8bb920b4","type":"paragraph","text":"斯天林：欧洲合众国U的口号是错误的。列宁发现后即取消了这一口号…..…","index":4,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"00236dd65f"},{"id":"3e3b9797dd","type":"paragraph","text":"我认为，变帝国主义战争为国内战争的口号（在第一次帝国主义世界大战时期）只对俄罗斯合适，在俄罗斯，工人与农民密切相连，在沙皇制度的条件下，他们能够强攻资产阶级。","index":5,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"00236dd65f"},{"id":"34faed6810","type":"paragraph","text":"对欧洲国家来说，这个口号就不合适了，因为在那些国家，工人从资产阶级那单得到了某些民主改单，被它们紧紧抓住，没有准备好走上内战（单命）的道路反对资产阶级。（必须用另外的方式对待欧洲工人。）","index":6,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"00236dd65f"},{"id":"9e8d8a952a","type":"paragraph","text":"必须注意欧洲工人的这些特点，以另外的方式提出问题，为他们提出另外的口号","index":7,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"00236dd65f"},{"id":"9fb0cea502","type":"paragraph","text":"在德国，小资产阶级民族主义者善于作剧烈的转变，他们没有同资本主义传统连在一起，与张伯伦一类的资产阶级领导人不同","index":8,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"00236dd65f"},{"id":"c0ccde152b","type":"paragraph","text":"①“欧洲合众国”的口号是布尔什维克在1914年10月的俄国社会民主工党（布）的宣言《战争和俄罗斯社会民主主义》中提出的。列宁曾在1915年发表的《论欧洲合众国口号》一文中批判过这个口号。","index":9,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"00236dd65f"},{"id":"df3fbd0874","type":"paragraph","text":"官主义墨守成规、老套，不进行独立思考，不吸收由于条件改变而出现的新东西··.·.·《季来特洛夫日记选编》","index":10,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"00236dd65f"},{"id":"63979cda32","type":"paragraph","text":"选自新编《斯大林全集》2002年版第102-103页","index":11,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"00236dd65f"},{"id":"bc051b88a8","type":"paragraph","text":"档案附卷干第14-15页","index":12,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"00236dd65f"}],"page":{"id":"36b9c67238","publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"00236dd65f","start":2761,"end":2762}}}},"__N_SSG":true}